name: Experiment Or Die #97
description:
Project to create a new collage every day for a year using my years of personal assets. The 9th official letter in The Cool Alphabet, S Is For Snake. From here on out edition numbers will match the quantities in Scrabble for each letter. 

Long time gamer and 1 of the franchises that I have followed the longest is Metal Gear and the ageless Solid Snake. First entry for me was Metal Gear Solid for Playstation, played 2 and 3, missed 4 when I was in college and bought my original PS4 so I could play Phantom Pain when it first came out. Not only are these some of my all time favorite games but Snake is by far one of my favorite characters. Twitter and IG: Nikejerk
